OL,5, The top official at the Treasury who   
OL,6, was sacked days after Liz Truss became 
OL,7, prime minister received an exit payout 
OL,8, of #335,000.                           
OL,10,FSir Tom Scholar was fired after Ms     
OL,11,FTruss pledged to change "Treasury      
OL,12,Forthodoxy" during the Tory leadership  
OL,13,Fcampaign last year.                    
OL,15,FHis dismissal was criticised by former 
OL,16,Fofficials, who said it was an attack on
OL,17,Fthe impartiality of the civil service. 
OL,19,FAt the time, the Treasury thanked Sir  
OL,20,FTom for his "dedicated service".       
